quran[7{c,v,t}:
6,125,pas ( yeh haqeeqat hai ke ) jisay Allah hadaayat bakhsnay ka iradah karta hai uss ka seenah islam ke liye khol deta hai aur jisay gumraahi mein daalnay ka iradah karta hai uss ke seenay ko tang kar deta hai aur aisa bhinchtahai ke ( islam ka tasawwur karte hi ) ussay yun maloom honay lagta hai ke goya is ki rooh aasman ki taraf parwaaz kar rahi hai iss terhan Allah ( haq se faraar aur nafrat ki ) napaaki unn logon par musallat kar deta hai jo imaan nahi laatay
6,126,halaank yeh rasta tumahray rab ka seedha rasta hai aur is ke nishanaat unn logon ke liye wazeh kar diye gay hain jo nasiyaat qubool karte hain
6,127,unn keliye unn ke rab ke paas salamti ka ghar hai aur woh un ka sir parast hai uss sahih tarz amal ki wajah se jo unhon ne ikhtiyar kya
6,128,"jis roz Allah un sab logon ko ghair kar jama kere ga, is roz woh junoo se khitaab kar ke farmaiye ga ke"" a y giroh jin! tum ne noo insani par khoob haath saaf kya"" insanon mein se jo unn ke Rafeeq thay woh arz karen ge"" parvar-digaar! hum mein se har aik ne dosray ko khoo bay istemaal kya hai, aur ab hum uss waqt par aa puhanche hain jo to ne hamaray liye muqarrar kar diya tha"" Allah farmaiye ga"" acha ab aag tumhara thikana hai, is mein tum hamesha raho ge"" a"" seen se bachchen ge sirf wohi jinhein Allah bachana chahay ga, be shak tumhara rab Dana aur Aleem hai"
6,129,"dekho, is terhan hum ( aakhir t- mein ) zaalmon ko aik dosray ka saathi banayen ge uss kamaai ki wajah se jo woh ( duniya mein aik dosray ke sath mil kar ) karte thay"
6,130,"( is mauqa par Allah un se pouchye ga ke )"" ae giroh jin o ins, kya tumahray paas khud tum hi mein se woh paighambar nahi aeye thay jo tum ko meri ayaat sunaate aur iss din ke injaam se darate thay ?"" woh kahin ge"" haan, hum apne khilaaf khud gawahi dete hain"" aaj duniya ki zindagi ne inn logon ko dhokay mein daal rakha hai, magar uss waqt woh khud apne khilaaf gawahi den ge ke woh kafir thay"
6,131,( yeh shahadat unn se is liye li jaye gi ke yeh saabit ho jaye ke ) tumhara rab bustiyon ko zulm ke sath tabah karne wala nah tha jabkay un ke bashinday haqeeqat se na waaqif hon
